com.javaweb.model

Class ModelAirlineCompany<T extends Aircraft>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.javaweb.model.ModelAirlineCompany<T>

  • public class ModelAirlineCompany<T extends Aircraft>
extends java.lang.Object
    ModelAirlineCompany.java

    Class that defines collection for all objects, that extends Aircraft. It is using for all tasks from the variant 9. Also here are some additional methods for deleting and adding airplanes to the container. Container - is TreeMap. It is used, because of easy filtering. Key - object with aircraft, value - quantity of such airplanes in the airline company.

    Since:
    18 Nov 2016
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Andrii Chernysh
